{"tid":1720492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［教育界集氣] 你為我們擋子彈，我願意為你罷工，教育界醒覺未？ 暴政殘殺孩子 我地仲沉默就=幫兇","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:37:55.000Z","uid":158830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"581a612c7a405798d86b281d0b893a09377780c6","tid":1720492,"uid":158830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTanjNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTanjNQ.jpg&h=73ec8815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🆘搜集教育界資料🚩🚩<br />\n即使教育局向外界表示接下來14/11-17/11會停課，請問有沒有同工認為如果政府依然漠視民意，沒有回應及遣責學生被警方暴力對待的行為，作為教師們未能為上到前線！但我們可以選擇教育界全體繼續罷工❗❗<br />\n<br />\n教師們❗我們還可以接受和沉默對待社會中每一個人所流的血和淚嗎？你們願意為我們擋子彈！我們願意為你罷工！！！！！！🆘🆘<br />\n<br />\n請以fb page 中的 投票方式表達教育界同工會繼續罷工以表達訴求！🆘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101323324668085/posts/103286231138461?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101323324668085%2Fposts%2F103286231138461%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=c0aef0ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101323324668085/posts/103286231138461?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8734ea1b1cc7c5220e7eb5055fff373b1c47c685","tid":1720492,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"周梓樂手足頭七<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1wBo4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1wBo4F.jpg&h=3452e01d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>他永遠停了在22歲。<br />\n你甘心他至今仍走得不明不白嗎？<br />\n他在天上也會安心嗎？</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suk2342.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsuk2342.png&h=07c123f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"185b67fb460abb22e56aedcc1590cca7288ede61","tid":172